title: WikiLeaks exposes Trump Groping plot phony
subtitle: Contrary to biased reports, the exchange of leaked e-mails in May 2016 between the employees of the DNA does not reveal a conspiracy to fabricate false accusations of "motilization" against Donald Trump.
author: David Emery
vclaim: The leaked e-mails from the DNC of May 2016 reveal a conspiracy to forge false stories about Donald Trump harassing women.
